GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE RESOLUTION 221
Sponsors: Senator Rabon (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to: Agriculture, Energy, and Environment
March 3, 2025
1 A SENATE RESOLUTION RELATING TO THE APPOINTMENT, NOMINATION, AND
2 CONFIRMATION OF PAMELA BREWINGTON CASHWELL AS SECRETARY OF
3 THE DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL AND CULTURAL RESOURCES.
4 Whereas, pursuant to G.S. 143B-9(a), the Governor shall notify the President of the
5 Senate of the name of each person to be nominated as head of a principal State department; and
6 Whereas, each nomination is subject to senatorial advice and consent in conformance
7 with Section 5(8) of Article III of the North Carolina Constitution; and
8 Whereas, the Governor has appointed Pamela Brewington Cashwell to serve as
9 Secretary of the Department of Natural and Cultural Resources pending further action by the
10 Senate; Now, therefore,
11 Be it resolved by the Senate:
12 SECTION 1. That the Senate shall hereby consider whether to confirm Pamela
13 Brewington Cashwell as Secretary of the Department of Natural and Cultural Resources.
14 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
*S221-v-1*

